ort findings you can support with the code that you are provided.\n        2. If you cannot quote specific code to justify a point, do not include it.\n        3. Do not infer intent from code that could have a plausible legitimate use.\n\n    You MUST return your answers in the following format.\n\n    It must be parseable as a json or a python list. DO NOT INCLUDE Markdown format like \"'''\" or 'json'.\n\n    \"\n\nRespond with ONLY the classification (e.g., 'conversational' or 'investigation:vuln_hunting'). Nothing else.", "timing": {"total_duration_seconds": 0.0025768280029296875}}
